r journey map, product catalog, brand voice guidelines\tComplete quiz script with questions, answer options, logic flows, and product tagging\t60%+ completion rate in testing, 50%+ email capture\tDays 6-8 1.5\tBuild Quiz in Platform\tQuiz Funnel Architect\tOpen quiz builder → Input questions from script → Connect products to answer choices → Design results page with recommendations → Set up thank you email → Configure Klaviyo integration\tQuiz script, product images, brand colors/fonts\tLive quiz accessible via link or embed code\tTest quiz completes successfully, email captured in Klaviyo\tDays 9-10 1.6\tCreate Quiz Landing Page\tLanding Page Conversion Specialist\tUse GemPages/Replo → Design above-fold section with quiz CTA → Add benefit-driven headlines → Include social proof (reviews, media logos) → Embed quiz inline or popup → Optimize for mobile 9:16 format\tQuiz embed code, brand assets, customer testimonials, trust badges\tCustom landing page with embedded quiz, mobile-optimized\tPage loads <2 sec, mobile responsive, CTA visible above fold\tDays 11-13 1.7\tSet Up Meta Pixel + Conversions API\tCustomer Data Platform Manager\tInstall Meta Pixel via Shopify → Configure standard events (ViewContent, AddToCart, Purchase, Lead) → Set up Conversions API via Elevar or native Shopify → Test events in Events Manager\tShopify admin access, Meta Business Manager access\tMeta Pixel firing correctly, CAPI connected, events showing in dashboard\tMatch quality >8.0/10, test purchases tracked correctly\tDays 14-15 1.8\tBuild First-Party Data Infrastructure\tCustomer Data Platform Manager\tInstall Segment or mParticle → Connect data sources (Shopify, Klaviyo, quiz app, Meta) → Create custom events for quiz completion, quiz abandonment → Build custom audiences in Meta\tAll platform API keys, data schema plan\tUnified customer data flowing to all platforms, custom audiences syncing to Meta\tReal-time data sync <5 min delay, audience sizes updating daily\tDays 16-18 1.9\tDesign 